---
title: Creamy Buffalo Chicken Salad with Cheddar, Croutons & Lemony Ranch Dressing
description: For beloved apps, Buffalo wings have few rivals. And it’s never been an everyday dish—until now! This salad features the dream team—Frank’s Hot Sauce + ranch dressing—plus it’s a dinner, lunch, or even brunch idea ready in under 30. Seared, chopped chicken is combined with a creamy-spicy Buffalo dressing, then gets scooped over a salad of crisp lettuce, celery, crunchy croutons, rich cheddar, and cooling lemon-ranch dressing. It wouldn’t be Buffalo without a drizzle of Frank’s Hot Sauce to finish.
